Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.input.csv

Class CsvInputChunkProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.input.csv.CsvInputChunkProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, CsvInputChunk, InputChunk
    public class CsvInputChunkProxy
extends Object
implements CsvInputChunk
    CsvInputChunk that adapts new input source groups during the streaming of data. InputIterator is fairly straight-forward, but is made a bit more complicated by the fact that there can be multiple different data streams. The outer iterator, CsvGroupInputIterator, is still responsible for handing out chunks, something that generally is good thing since it solves a bunch of other problems. The problem it has is that it doesn't know exactly which type of CsvInputChunk it wants to create, because that's up to each input group. This gap is bridged here in this class.
